<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Goodbye</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="stars"></div>

<div class="container">

    <h1 class="title">Goodbye 👋</h1>

    <h2 id="typing"></h2>

    <div class="message">
        <p>
            Every ending becomes the beginning of a new journey.
        </p>

        <p>
            Thank you for every smile, every conversation,
            every laugh, every lesson, and every unforgettable memory.
        </p>

        <p>
            Time may take us to different places,
            but the moments we shared will always remain close to my heart.
        </p>

        <p>
            Distance may separate us,
            but memories never fade.
        </p>

        <p>
            I sincerely wish you happiness,
            success,
            good health,
            and a beautiful future.
        </p>

        <p class="last">
            This isn't forever...
            It's simply
            <br><br>
            <span>See You Again ❤️</span>
        </p>
    </div>

</div>

<script src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>